	   <tr><td colspan=2>I hate &quot;this is a XXXClass item&quot; posts. Honestly. But, any guild that lets anyone other than a ranger loot this bow (assuming of course they all don't have it) is doing itself a major disservice. I cringe when i see Warriors looting 30/40 bows in DN. This is just an amplification of that.<br><br>Warriors pull with bows, that's IT. One shot, and done. The ONLY stat that matters is Range. <br><br>Rangers, on the other hand, get Trueshot. With a good bow (or maybe an Uber one like this) they will dish huge damage in Raid encounters, at range so as to be unaffected by AoE attacks (See post above, 20k damage to VS in 1 fight - and you just know he was never lifetapped. Hell, he was probably on the balcony...)<br>&nbsp;<br>Arynduil<br>A Pathfinder on EMarr<br><br>"In a crowded Universe, when the talking turns to noise, you almost start laughing"</td></tr>
